    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>Azalea Estates of Fayetteville is committed to ensuring that our website is accessible to all users, including those using assistive technologies. We strive to meet or exceed the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA.</p>

    <h2>On-Site Accessibility</h2>
    <p>Our single-story campus is designed without elevators or stairs. Every common area, dining space, wellness facility, and residence is fully accessible. Wheelchair-accessible pathways connect all buildings and gardens.</p>

    <h2>Ongoing Efforts</h2>
    <p>We continually review and improve the accessibility of our digital and physical spaces. If you encounter any barriers or have suggestions for improvement, we&rsquo;d appreciate hearing from you.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>To report an accessibility issue, request information in an alternate format, or share feedback, please call {{ site.contact.phone }} or email <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a>.</p>
